<h1 id="列表">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%88%97%e8%a1%a8"></a>
列表
</h1><ul>
<li>无序列表
<ul>
<li>短横线+一个空格</li>
<li>tab+短横线+一个空格使这一行作为上一行子列表元素</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>有序列表
<ol>
<li>数字+小数点+一个空格</li>
<li>同样tab+数字+小数点+一个空格缩进一行</li>
<li></li>
</ol>
</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="图片">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%9b%be%e7%89%87"></a>
图片
</h1><ul>
<li>$$![Engelbart](图片网址)$$</li>
<li>![[Pasted image 20230625203344.png]]</li>
<li>调整宽度
<ul>
<li>$$![Engelbart|100](图片链接)$$</li>
<li>![[Pasted image 20230625203536.png]]</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="外部链接">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%a4%96%e9%83%a8%e9%93%be%e6%8e%a5"></a>
外部链接
</h1><h3 id="指向库中笔记图片">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e6%8c%87%e5%90%91%e5%ba%93%e4%b8%ad%e7%ac%94%e8%ae%b0%e5%9b%be%e7%89%87"></a>
指向库中笔记/图片
</h3><ul>
<li>$http://obsidian.md - automatic!$
<ul>
<li><em>指向网络链接，以网址显示，$仅为排版美观</em></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>$[obsidian](http://obsidian.md)$
<ul>
<li><em>指向网络连接，以中括号内内容显示</em></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="obsidian-url">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#obsidian-url"></a>
Obsidian URL
</h3><p>Obsidian URI 通常采用以下形式：
</p>
$$obsidian://action?param1=value&param2=value$$<p>
action表示执行操作，value为参数
比如打开笔记：
</p>
$$[标注的笔记名，想给的代号](obsidian://open?path=笔记绝对路径)$$<p>
<strong>注意中英文括号、冒号</strong>
举例：
<a href="#ZgotmplZ">打开高数</a>
其中，path接文件绝对路径</p>
<ul>
<li><em>打开某库，不打开具体文件只打开文件夹不显示效果</em>
$$[name](obsidian://open?vault=库文件夹名称/库ID)$$
<a href="#ZgotmplZ">打开笔记文件夹</a></li>
<li><em>打开Math文件夹下的高数，<strong>.md</strong>拓展名可不写</em>
<a href="#ZgotmplZ">高数</a></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="others">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#others"></a>
Others
</h3><ul>
<li>
<p>URL中有空格时需要转义为$\%20$</p>
<ul>
<li>上面%20的百分号%需要转义，%</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p>或者用&lt;&gt;将有空格内容包围</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>引用
</p>
$$> 引用内容$$<p>
</p>
$$\ 引用来源$$<p>
eg</p>
</li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p>时间是一场有去无回的旅行，好的坏的都是风景。
\ ——《岁月神偷》金玟岐</p></blockquote>
<ul>
<li>
<p>行内代码
<code>include&lt;stdc++.h&gt;</code></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>代码块
<em>Obsidian 会将六个反引号括起来的内容识别为代码块，并将其按代码格式显示。代码块支持语法高亮功能，你可以在代码块的第一行（即开头处的反引号后）声明语言来使用特定的语法高亮。</em></p>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-C++" data-lang="C++"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="cp">#include&lt;stdc++.h&gt;
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="cp"></span><span class="k">using</span> <span class="k">namespace</span> <span class="n">std</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kt">int</span> <span class="nf">main</span><span class="p">(){</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="kt">int</span> <span class="n">a</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">for</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">int</span> <span class="n">b</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">b</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">b</span><span class="o">++</span><span class="p">){</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="n">a</span><span class="o">+=</span><span class="n">b</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="n">cont</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="n">endl</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Percent-encoding">更多编码规范</a></p>
